<concept id="concept_vmf_5s4_m3c">
    <title>6. Beta Testing</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>Before launch, a <b>structured beta test</b> was conducted.</p>
        <p>Participants were asked to complete a scripted set of tasks to evaluate:</p>
        <ul id="ul_ur3_5s4_m3c">
            <li>
                <p>navigation</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>search behavior</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>content discoverability</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>upload workflows</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>Feedback from the beta phase informed final adjustments before production release.</p>
    </conbody>
</concept>
